" doc: Yank until end of line
nnoremap Y y$

" Clear search results with <Esc>
nnoremap <esc> :nohlsearch<cr>
" doc: Leave insert mode
inoremap jk <esc>

" doc: Incremental search
nnoremap s /
" doc: Incremental search - reverse
nnoremap S ?



